Researcher 1 refers to a researcher with a unique identifier of 1 in the experiment_researchers table; 
An experiment is considered to have "multiple runs" if it has more than 2 runs; 
A run is considered to be "after 2022" if its start date is after January 1, 2022.

sql:
SELECT file_size 
FROM files 
WHERE file_name = (SELECT file_name FROM files WHERE file_path = '/path/to/file1.xlsx');

SELECT COUNT(*) AS total_researchers
FROM experiment_researchers
WHERE experiment_id = 0;

SELECT e.name
FROM experiments e
WHERE e.principal_investigator = (
  SELECT r.name FROM researchers r WHERE r.researcher_id = 1
);
